% JEPA-WORM Phase 0 — Bibliography
%
% Every dataset, baseline-reference paper, and external method used by the
% project gets a stable BibTeX entry here. Auto-included in publishable
% reports rendered by `wormjepa report` (Epic 7 Story 7.8).
%
% Datasets are populated in Epic 2 Story 2.3 (data/SOURCES.md mirror).
% Method references are populated as each module imports them.
%
% Format: standard BibTeX. The pre-commit hook (after Epic 4) checks this file
% parses without errors via bibtexparser.
%
% Entry-key convention: lowercase, kebab-case, suffixed with the canonical
% publication year (e.g. ``vjepa2-2025``, ``flavell-2023``).
%
% Entries with ``note = "citation needed — verify against ..."`` are
% placeholders where the canonical reference has not been independently
% confirmed by the authoring agent. Verify before quoting in any
% reportable artefact.

